leve.name: Watching the Western Wall
leve.description: While the knights move forward with their plans to set up watchtowers along the western side of the hinterlands, the location appears to be far too removed from any roads along which house caravans can bring necessary supplies. I want you to survey the land and ascertain what resources we can freely use to fortify our positions and which will have to be brought in by airship with a dedicated guard.
leve.client: Temple Knights Second Commander Ser Handeloup
